### =================================================================================
### PERSON 3 — END TO END TESTING SCRIPT
### Prequisite: Start with a clear database, or just new emails for testing.
### Scenario: Admin creates a course, lesson, quiz, and questions (Person 1 & 2 actions).
### Then Learner signs up, browses courses, enrolls, watches lessons, calculates progress, attempts a quiz, and leaves a review.
### =================================================================================

# Global Variables
@admin_email = admin@learnova.com
@admin_pass = Admin@1234

@learner_email = learner@learnova.com
@learner_pass = Learner@1234



### =================================================================================
### PART 1: DB SEEDING (PERSON 1 & 2)
### =================================================================================

### 1(a). Register Admin/Instructor
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Instructor",
  "email": "{{admin_email}}",
  "password": "{{admin_pass}}"
}

### 1(b). Login Admin
# @name adminLogin
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{admin_email}}",
  "password": "{{admin_pass}}"
}

### Store Admin Token
@admin_token = {{adminLogin.response.body.token}}

### 1(c). Create a Course
# @name createCourse
POST http://localhost:5000/api/courses
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Mastering frontend",
  "description": "frontend",
  "shortDesc": "mast frontend",
  "visibility": "EVERYONE",
  "accessRule": "OPEN",
  "tags": [] 
}

### Store Course ID
@course_id = {{createCourse.response.body.data.id}}

### 1(d). Publish the Course
PATCH http://localhost:5000/api/courses/{{course_id}}/publish
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isPublished": true,
  "websiteUrl": "https://example.com/course"
}

### 1(e). Create a Lesson (Using Multipart Form-Data without actual file)
# @name createLesson
POST http://localhost:5000/api/courses/{{course_id}}/lessons
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="title"

Introduction to Node
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="type"

VIDEO
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="order"

1
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### Store Lesson ID
@lesson_id = {{createLesson.response.body.data.id}}

### 1(f). Create a Quiz
# @name createQuiz
POST http://localhost:5000/api/courses/{{course_id}}/quizzes
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Module 1 Assessment",
  "description": "Final assessment for the first module."
}

### Store Quiz ID
@quiz_id = {{createQuiz.response.body.id}}

### 1(g). Create a Question for the Quiz
# @name createQuestion
POST http://localhost:5000/api/quizzes/{{quiz_id}}/questions
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Node.js is single-threaded.",
  "order": 1
}

### Store Question ID
@question_id = {{createQuestion.response.body.id}}

### 1(h). Create Correct Option for Question
# @name createOption
POST http://localhost:5000/api/questions/{{question_id}}/options
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "True",
  "isCorrect": true,
  "order": 1
}

### Store Option ID
@option_id = {{createOption.response.body.id}}

### 1(i). Create Incorrect Option for Question
POST http://localhost:5000/api/questions/{{question_id}}/options
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "False",
  "isCorrect": false,
  "order": 2
}

### 1(j). Set Rewards for the Quiz
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/quizzes/{{quiz_id}}/rewards
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rewards": [
    { "attemptNumber": 1, "points": 100 },
    { "attemptNumber": 2, "points": 50 }
  ]
}


### =================================================================================
### PART 2: PERSON 3 (LEARNER JOURNEY)
### =================================================================================

### 2(a). Register Learner
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Leo",
  "lastName": "Learner",
  "email": "{{learner_email}}",
  "password": "{{learner_pass}}"
}

### 2(b). Login Learner
# @name learnerLogin
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{learner_email}}",
  "password": "{{learner_pass}}"
}

### Store Learner Token
@learner_token = {{learnerLogin.response.body.token}}


### 3. COURSE DISCOVERY & VIEWING
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------

### Browse Published Courses
# @name publishedCourses
GET http://localhost:5000/api/courses/published
Authorization: Bearer {{learner_token}}


### Get Course Details
GET http://localhost:5000/api/courses/{{course_id}}/detail
Authorization: Bearer {{learner_token}}


### 4. ENROLLMENTS & PAYMENTS
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------

### Enroll in Course (AccessRule is OPEN)
# @name enrollInfo
POST http://localhost:5000/api/enrollments
Authorization: Bearer {{learner_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "courseId": "{{course_id}}"
}

### Get User's Active Enrollments (My Courses Page)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/enrollments/my
Authorization: Bearer {{learner_token}}

### Get Course Progress for Enrollment
# Assume enrollmentId from above
@enrollment_id = {{enrollInfo.response.body.data.id}}

GET http://localhost:5000/api/enrollments/{{enrollment_id}}/progress
Authorization: Bearer {{learner_token}}


### 5. PLAYER & PROGRESS
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------

### Load Lesson for Player
GET http://localhost:5000/api/player/{{course_id}}/{{lesson_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{learner_token}}

### Mark Lesson as Started / Completed (Records Progress)
PATCH http://localhost:5000/api/progress/lesson/{{lesson_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{learner_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isCompleted": true,
  "timeSpentSeconds": 180,
  "enrollmentId": "{{enrollment_id}}"
}

### Get updated course progress showing this completed lesson
GET http://localhost:5000/api/enrollments/{{enrollment_id}}/progress
Authorization: Bearer {{learner_token}}


### 6. QUIZ ATTEMPTS & ANSWERS
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------

### Start a New Quiz Attempt
# @name startAttempt
POST http://localhost:5000/api/quizzes/{{quiz_id}}/attempt
Authorization: Bearer {{learner_token}}

### Store Attempt ID
@attempt_id = {{startAttempt.response.body.id}}

### Submit Answer for the Question
POST http://localhost:5000/api/attempts/{{attempt_id}}/answer
Authorization: Bearer {{learner_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "questionId": "{{question_id}}",
  "selectedOptionId": "{{option_id}}"
}

### Complete Quiz Attempt (Triggers scoring and awarding of Points & Badges)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/attempts/{{attempt_id}}/complete
Authorization: Bearer {{learner_token}}


### 7. REVIEWS
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------

### Add a Review for the Course
POST http://localhost:5000/api/courses/{{course_id}}/reviews
Authorization: Bearer {{learner_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rating": 5,
  "comment": "This module was excellent! Detailed and very practical to learn from."
}

### List Course Reviews (Should show newly added review and updated average score)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/courses/{{course_id}}/reviews
Authorization: Bearer {{learner_token}}
